  "description": "<i>Casino Roulette</i> is a Las Vegas style roulette game for up to eight players.\nEvery player starts with 5000 on hand and the game ends when the last human player runs out of cash. \nThe main game screen consists of the standard standard Las Vegas roulette betting table. When all the bets have been placed and the option &quot;Spin Wheel&quot; is selected an animation of a spinning roulette wheel is displayed and then the results shows up. After that the table has to be cleared before new bets can be placed. The players can view wheel and player statistics any time during the betting phase.",
